                        </h3>
                        <div class="id_place" style="width:355px">
                        <div class="box int_id">
                            <input type="text" id="id" class="int" maxlength="20" placeholder="아이디" required style="width:330px">
                        </div>
                        <div class="btn_wrap">
                        <button type="button" onclick="id_check()">중복 확인</button>
                        </div>
                        </div>
                        <span class="error_next_box"></span>
                        <br>- 아이디 중복확인
                    </div>
    
                    <!-- PW1 -->
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="join_title"><label for="pswd1"><img src="images/asterisk.png" style="width:8px;position:relative;top:5px;margin-right:2px">비밀번호</label></h3>
                        <span class="box int_pass">
                            <input type="password" id="pswd1" class="int" maxlength="20" placeholder="비밀번호" required>
                            <span id="alertTxt">사용불가</span>
                            <img src="images/m_icon_pass.png" id="pswd1_img1" class="pswdImg">
                        </span>
                        <span class="error_next_box"></span>
                        <p>- 10자 이상 입력</p>
                        <p>- 영문/숫자/특수문자 2개 이상 조합</p>
                    </div>
    
                    <!-- PW2 -->
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="join_title"><label for="pswd2"><img src="images/asterisk.png" style="width:8px;position:relative;top:5px;margin-right:2px">비밀번호 확인</label></h3>
                        <span class="box int_pass_check">
                            <input type="password" id="pswd2" class="int" maxlength="20" placeholder="비밀번호 재확인" required>
                            <img src="images/m_icon_check_disable.png" id="pswd2_img1" class="pswdImg">
                        </span>
                        <span class="error_next_box"></span>
                    </div>
    
                    <!-- NAME -->
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="join_title"><label for="name"><img src="images/asterisk.png" style="width:8px;position:relative;top:5px;margin-right:2px">이메일</label></h3>
                        <span class="box int_name">
                            <input type="text" id="name" class="int" maxlength="20" required>
                        </span>
                        <span class="images/error_next_box"></span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="join_title"><label for="addr"><img src="images/asterisk.png" style="width:8px;position:relative;top:5px;margin-right:2px">주소</label></h3>
                        <span class="box int_addr">
                            <input type="text" id="addr" class="int" maxlength="80">
                        </span>
                        <span class="images/error_next_box"></span>
                    </div>
    
                    <div style="padding-bottom:34px">
                        <h3 class="join_title"><label for="r_id">추천인 아이디</label></h3>
                        <span class="box int_r_id">
                            <input type="text" id="email" class="int" maxlength="100" placeholder="선택입력">
                        </span>
                        <span class="error_next_box">이메일 주소를 다시 확인해주세요.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="terms">
                    <p><img src="images/asterisk.png" style="width:8px;position:relative;top:5px;margin-right:2px"><span>이용약관동의</span></p>
                    <p><input type="checkbox"><span>전체 동의합니다.</span></p>
                    <p class="gray">선택 항목에 동의하지 않은 경우도 회원가입 및 일반적인 서비스를 이용할 수 있습니다.</p>
                    <ul class="terms_web">
                        <li><input type="checkbox" required>이용약관 <span>(필수)</span><a href="#"><img class="leftarrow" src="./images/arrow_ico_join.png" alt="화살표" style="width:7px;position:relative;margin-left:130px"></a></li>
                        <li><input type="checkbox" required> 개인정보처리방침 <span>(필수)</span><a href="#"><img class="leftarrow" src="./images/arrow_ico_join.png" alt="화살표" style="width:7px;position:relative;margin-left:80px"></a></li>
                        <li><input type="checkbox" required>본인은 만 14세 이상입니다. <span>(필수)</span><a href="#"><img class="leftarrow" src="./images/arrow_ico_join.png" alt="화살표" style="width:7px;position:relative;margin-left:36px"></a></li>
                        <li><input type="checkbox">마케팅 수신동의 <span>(선택)</span><input type="checkbox">이메일<input type="checkbox">문자<img class="leftarrow" src="./images/downarrow_ico_main.png" alt="화살표" style="width:10px;height:8px;;position:relative;margin-left:-5px;top:10px"><a href="#"></a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
    
                <!-- JOIN BTN-->
                <div class="btn_area" style="margin-top:20px">
                    <button type="button" id="btnJoin">
                        <span>가입하기</span>
                    </button>
                </div>
              </div>
            <!-- content-->
         </div>
        <!-- wrapper -->
    </div>
